comments: Aldama (MEM) contests the jump shot attempt by Simons (POR) and initiates contact to his lower body, affecting his ability to return to the floor.
Walker (POR) slides alongside of Williams Jr. (MEM) on the perimeter and when marginal contact occurs, Williams Jr. loses control of the ball.
Williams Jr. (MEM) attempts to release the shot before the shot clock expires and any contact by Camara (POR) is marginal.
Williams Jr. (MEM) reaches across Hagans' (POR) front, but Hagans moves through the contact in transition.
Williams Jr. (MEM) veers slightly into Camara (POR) and marginal contact occurs as the two players come together.
Walker (POR) deflects the ball out of bounds.
Williams Jr. (MEM) extends his elbow into Camara's (POR) face and after communicating with the Replay Center, the foul is deemed a flagrant foul, penalty 1.
